data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT PLUS $5,000 SELLER CONCESSION*** Great location in South Daytona, just a 5 minute drive to beaches and 10 minute drive to all Daytona attractions. Located on a quiet neighborhood with an elementary school at walking distance. This home features beautiful hardwood floors throughout the entire house. Fully renovated bathrooms, newer appliances. Large screened porch with a fenced in yard. Lots of square footage with a spacious family room on the back of the home. There is 1 car garage with a back door access to the porch. This home is move in ready, great for families or investment opportunity. This home is a must see!
